data.description: Check Out This Adorable Ranch In a cul-de-sac with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths & a Bonus Room! Over 1900 Square Feet With Tons of Upgrades! Open Floor Plan with Vaulted Ceilings, Built-In Entertainment Center & Gas Log Fireplace. Backyard Oasis Includes Screened Porch With Tile Floors Leading to Private and Oversized Back Deck. Updates Include Roof with Architectural Shingles (2022), LVP Flooring (2021), Crawlspace Encapsulation (2023), Kitchen Appliances (2016), Light Fixtures, Fresh Paint. Amenities Include The Clubhouse, Community Pool, Playground, Fitness Center & More! Welcome Home! AGENTS-NOT member of LLP MLS? Call Showing Time to schedule and let them know you are NOT a member and need access.
